OL,3,CMan denies murder of young mother shot
OL,4,Coutside bar
OL,6,FA man has denied murdering a mother-of-
OL,7,Fone who was shot outside a bar in
OL,8,FSheffield.
OL,10,FJemele Rhone, 30, is charged with the
OL,11,Fmurder of 30-year-old Shanice Brookes,
OL,12,Fwho was shot near the One Four One bar
OL,13,Fin West Street, in the city centre,
OL,14,Fshortly before 2.45am on 25 May.
OL,16,FMs Brookes was described by police as
OL,17,Fan "innocent bystander".
OL,26,@yD@DOUyD@WO]
