OL,3,CMan denies murder of young mother shot
OL,4,Coutside bar
OL,6,FRhone, of Outram Road, Sheffield,
OL,7,Fappeared at Sheffield Crown Court on
OL,8,FMonday, where he pleaded not guilty to
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,FHe also denied wounding another person
OL,12,Fwith intent, and possessing criminal
OL,13,Fcash.
OL,15,FRhone pleaded guilty to a charge of
OL,16,Fpossessing a handgun.
OL,18,FAll charges related to the same day.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
