OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784638109
OL,3,CMan denies murder of young mother shot
OL,4,Coutside bar
OL,6,FRhone attended the hearing via
OL,7,Fvideolink from prison, and wore a face
OL,8,Fmask, which he was asked to remove
OL,9,Fwhen he confirmed his name and gave
OL,10,Fhis pleas to the charges.
OL,12,FJudge Jeremy Richardson KC set a trial
OL,13,Fdate of 18 January 2027 at an earlier
OL,14,Fhearing.
OL,16,FRhone's co-defendant, Deiryen Dyce,
OL,17,F32, of Ellesmere Road North,
OL,18,FSheffield, appeared in court on Monday.
